*   The [Alfaro 155 hp 4-cylinder barrel engine](/Swashplate_engine). Barrel engines, with their unique swashplate or camplate mechanisms, were an alternative to conventional piston engines, promising compactness and reduced vibration. This particular design from Alfaro was a bold engineering choice.

