[Alvis Car and Engineering Company](/Alvis_Car_and_Engineering_Company), a British firm known for its luxury cars and military vehicles, also ventured into the design and manufacture of radial aircraft engines. Their engines, often named after mythological figures, were known for their robust construction and powerful output.

